message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with audio and music signal processing. cs.CV is also likely as it involves image processing and alignment of sheet music images. cs.CL is another possibility as it involves natural language processing for text recognition in sheet music. cs.LG is also possible as it involves the use of neural networks for cross-modality embedding spaces. cs.IR is less likely but still possible as it involves information retrieval for matching audio queries with sheet music databases.
